Class OnlineStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • OnlineStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Store

    public class OnlineStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements Store
    A class that represents the Online Store of a company. It has it's own stock and number. There can be only one Online Store in a company that is why if more than one Online Store is created, it will not have any affect.
